                      <img src="images/icon_mi_1.gif" width="15" height="15" border="0" alt="" title="" hspace="3" /><font color="#000000" face="arial" size="2">Posted&nbsp;-&nbsp;08/21/2003&nbsp;:&nbsp; 2:26:50 PM</font>
